[inaudible] representation,

00:45:42.160 --> 00:45:44.140
then how much higher the
pedestal is, so to speak,

00:45:44.140 --> 00:45:47.440
that you are then placed
on as the representative

00:45:47.440 --> 00:45:49.300
of all Asian-Americans.

00:45:49.300 --> 00:45:52.570
And I think, also, when we
