But, it is something that I --

00:59:24.180 --> 00:59:26.520
You know, have learned to
take very seriously and not

00:59:26.520 --> 00:59:32.620
like something that I am going
to do because I think it's easy,

00:59:32.620 --> 00:59:35.580
