01:01:06.020 --> 01:01:10.560
the two really adapt to
one another and it's often

01:01:10.560 --> 01:01:13.900
in the most tragic moments that
like [inaudible] like a dash

01:01:13.900 --> 01:01:17.040
of comedy can make
things even more powerful.

01:01:17.040 --> 01:01:21.710
